# Hardware safety

- Default to the lowest practical speed / duty.
- End every motion script with stop / neutral (chassis stop, arm safe pose).
- Prefer short timed moves over `while True` without a clear exit.
- Assume UART may be misconfigured on a fresh image until `dtoverlay=uart0-pi5` is confirmed.
- Do not enable gripper close commands in tight loops while debugging.
